---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-layout fade-in">
      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="section-label">About me</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Engineer, architect,<br />builder.</h2>
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>
            I'm a Solutions Architect with 10+ years turning complex research into
            production systems. My work spans AI, data engineering, and R&D leadership
            across Brazil, Germany, Austria, Portugal, and the Netherlands.
          </p>
          <p>
            I've led cross-continental teams, built autonomous drone systems,
            designed knowledge graphs at scale, and driven digital transformation
            across 50+ locations. I thrive at the intersection of deep technical
            work and strategic impact.
          </p>
          <p>
            When I'm not architecting systems, you'll find me exploring new
            research papers, contributing to open source, or mentoring the next
            generation of engineers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <span class="highlight-number">10+</span>
          <span class="highlight-label">Years of experience</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <span class="highlight-number">5</span>
          <span class="highlight-label">Countries worked in</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <span class="highlight-number">50+</span>
          <span class="highlight-label">Locations transformed</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: var(--section-padding);
    background: var(--color-bg-dark);
  }

  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about .section-label,
  .about .section-title {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .about .section-label {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-highlights {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .highlight-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-dark-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .highlight-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .highlight-number {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .highlight-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted-light);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
